  <h2>Container Queries</h2>
  <p>Allows any element with both size & layout containment to be queried using a new <code>@container</code> rule, with similar syntax to existing media-queries.</p>
  <div class="fragment fade">
    <pre><code data-trim class="hlcss disable-line-numbers" data-line-numbers="1-3|5-9">
      .container {
        contain: layout inline-size style;
      }

      @container (min-width: 500px) {
        .container__content {
          /* ... */
        }
      }
    </code></pre>
  </div>
</section>

